    """The Fib4 number sequence is a sequence similar to the Fibbonacci sequnece that's defined as follows:\n
        fib4(0) -> 0\n
        fib4(1) -> 0\n
        fib4(2) -> 2\n
        fib4(3) -> 0\n
        fib4(n) -> fib4(n-1) + fib4(n-2) + fib4(n-3) + fib4(n-4).
    """
